# Indigo Design System â€” AI Implementation Rules

You are building UI for the Indigo e-commerce dashboard. Follow these rules strictly. No exceptions.

## Stack
Next.js 16 + Tailwind CSS v4 + Geist font + OKLCH tokens + shadcn/ui components.

## Spatial Grid â€” 4px base
All spacing is multiples of 4px. Use Tailwind spacing: 1=4px, 2=8px, 3=12px, 4=16px, 6=24px, 8=32px.

- Card padding: `p-4` (never p-5, p-6, p-8)
- Grid gap between cards: `gap-3`
- Section vertical spacing: `space-y-4`
- Layout padding: `p-4 md:p-6`
- List item: `px-3 py-2`
- Table cell: `px-3 py-2.5`

## Component Heights
All interactive elements use a unified height scale:
- xs (24px/h-6): badges, tags, tiny icon buttons
- **sm (32px/h-8): DEFAULT for dashboard** â€” buttons, inputs, selects
- md (36px/h-9): icon containers in cards
- lg (40px/h-10): settings page CTAs only, never in dashboard

Dashboard buttons: ALWAYS `size="sm"`. Never `size="default"` or `size="lg"`.
Icon buttons: `size="icon-sm"` (32Ã—32). Never `size="icon"` (40Ã—40).

## Typography â€” exactly 5 sizes
| Role | Class |
|------|-------|
| Page title | `text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight` (20px, one per page) |
| Stat value | `.stat-value` (28px/600/tabular-nums) |
| Section title | `text-sm font-semibold` (14px) |
| Body | `text-sm` or `text-sm font-medium` (14px) |
| Caption | `text-xs text-muted-foreground` (12px) |
| Stat label | `.stat-label` (11px/600/uppercase/tracked) |

BANNED: `text-base`, `text-lg`, `text-2xl`, `text-3xl`, `text-4xl`, `font-bold`.

## Border Radius â€” 3 values only
- `rounded-sm` (4px): badges, tags
- `rounded-md` (6px): buttons, inputs
- `rounded-lg` (8px): cards, dialogs, popovers
- `rounded-full`: avatars and status dots only

BANNED: `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`.

## Icon Containers
- Card/alert icons: `h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-{color}/10`
- Feed/list icons: `h-8 w-8 rounded-full`
- Empty state icons: `h-10 w-10 rounded-xl`
- Step indicators: `h-6 w-6 rounded-full`
- Inline icons: `h-4 w-4` (no container)

## Card Pattern
Cards override default shadcn Card padding:
```tsx
<Card className="py-0 gap-0">
  <div className="p-4">
    <h3 className="text-sm font-semibold">Title</h3>
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</Card>
```
- Never use `<CardContent>` with `py-0` cards (double padding)
- Never add `border-border` (Card has built-in `ring-1 ring-foreground/10`)
- Never add `shadow-*` to cards

## Colors â€” semantic only
Use semantic Tailwind classes, never raw OKLCH values:
- `text-primary`, `bg-primary`, `bg-primary/10`
- `text-success`, `bg-success/10`
- `text-warning`, `bg-warning/10`
- `text-error`, `bg-error/10`
- `text-info`, `bg-info/10`
- `text-muted-foreground` for secondary text

## Empty States
- Metric value 0: show `0` not `â‚¹0` for counts (use `isCurrency: false`)
- Chart no data: centered muted text "No data yet"
- Table no rows: icon (h-10) + heading + description + optional CTA

## Buttons
- Dashboard: always `size="sm"`, variant `default`/`outline`/`ghost`
- Destructive: `variant="destructive" size="sm"`
- Table row actions: `variant="ghost" size="icon-sm"`
- No custom height overrides (`className="h-7"` etc.)

## Banned Patterns
- Emoji in UI â†’ use Lucide icons
- `p-6`/`p-8` inside cards â†’ `p-4`
- `gap-6` between cards â†’ `gap-3`
- `h-12 w-12` card icons â†’ `h-9 w-9`
- `h-10 w-10` list icons â†’ `h-8 w-8`
- `<CardHeader>` + `<CardContent>` in compact cards â†’ single `<div className="p-4">`
- `shadow-sm`/`shadow-md` on cards â†’ remove

## File Conventions
- `"use server"` files cannot export types â€” put types in sibling `types.ts`
- Auth: `const { user, supabase } = await getAuthenticatedClient()`
- Always verify: `npx tsc --noEmit` = 0 errors after changes

## Interaction Patterns
- Command palette: already wired to âŒ˜K in dashboard-header.tsx â€” add new routes there
- Keyboard shortcuts: G+key for navigation, C for create â€” skip when input focused
- Breadcrumbs: add new routes to `routeConfig` and `parentRoutes` in dashboard-header.tsx
- Charts: always pair with a one-line summary sentence below the title
- Empty states: use `<EmptyState hint="Press C to create" />` â€” no decorative illustrations
- List pages: use `<PageHeader>` from `@/components/dashboard` for consistent headers
- Table secondary data: use `.text-secondary-data` (13px muted) or `.text-data-mono` (13px tabular-nums)
